This project is an optimized rewrite of the WeChat-to-Obsidian workflow described by:

- Jane-xiaoer/wechat-to-obsidian
- zhuyansen/wx-favorites-report

The SQLCipher key-capture method uses the public CCKeyDerivationPBKDF / Frida approach credited in those projects. Use this project only with WeChat data from accounts and devices you own or are explicitly authorized to process.
